description: Erection of a three- to six-storey residential block comprising 66 dwellings, consisting of 20 x one-bedroom flats, 10 x two-bedroom flats, 22 x three-bedroom flats, 13 x four-bedroom flats and 1 x five-bedroom dwellinghouse, including associated hard and soft landscaping and on-street car-parking within the curtilage of Stonebridge site 4B, subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 21/08/2008 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended)
